Concepts to learn in React js 
1. core of react (state or UI manipulation, JSX).
2.component reusability.
3. reusing of component(props).
4.how to propagate change(hooks).

Additional addons on react js 
1. Routers 
2. State Management 
3. Redux , redux toolkit, Zustand, Context Api
4. class based components

Note: There are many things that react cannot do such as seo , browse render of js, no routing.

We can learn Nextjs a framework based on react where can work on both frontend and backend.